title: AIIMS Nagpur Recruitment 2025 - Apply Online for 73 Senior Resident Posts
description: The All India Institute of Medical Sciences, Nagpur (AIIMS Nagpur) has declared the official notification for 2025. To fill up the vacancies for 73 Senior Resident Jobs. Those candidates who have qualified in the MS/ MD can grab this chance and apply for the AIIMS Nagpur Recruitment 2025 . Here we include the age limit, selection process, salary structure, education details, application fee, and how to apply for these posts.
